{"id":4282,"date":"2022-08-05T09:17:43","date_gmt":"2022-08-05T02:17:43","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/?p=4282"},"modified":"2022-08-05T09:31:56","modified_gmt":"2022-08-05T02:31:56","slug":"toan-10-sach-giao-khoa-giai-bai-tap-toan-10-file-loai-sach-moi","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/blog\/2022\/08\/05\/toan-10-sach-giao-khoa-giai-bai-tap-toan-10-file-loai-sach-moi\/","title":{"rendered":"To\u00e1n 10: S\u00e1ch gi\u00e1o khoa + gi\u1ea3i b\u00e0i t\u1eadp to\u00e1n 10 (file lo\u1ea1i s\u00e1ch m\u1edbi)"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Xin ch\u00e0o c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n! M\u00ecnh l\u00e0 Th\u1ecf v\u00e0 m\u00ecnh l\u1ea1i \u0111\u0103ng t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e2y \u1ea1!<\/p>\n<p>C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n bi\u1ebft h\u1ebft c\u1ea3 r\u1ed3i: L\u00e0 t\u1eeb n\u0103m h\u1ecdc 2022 &#8211; 2023 t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, B\u1ed9 gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u tri\u1ec3n khai ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh s\u00e1ch gi\u00e1o khoa m\u1edbi. Ngo\u00e0i vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecdc sinh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ef1 ch\u1ecdn c\u00e1c m\u00f4n h\u1ecdc y\u00eau th\u00edch th\u00ec c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ef1 ch\u1ecdn b\u1ed9 s\u00e1ch gi\u00e1o khoa d\u00f9ng trong gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y. Vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng g\u00e2y nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi c\u1ea3 h\u1ecdc sinh l\u1eabn gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean.<\/p>\n<p>V\u1ec1 thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i, vi\u1ec7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng song song nhi\u1ec1u b\u1ed9 s\u00e1ch s\u1ebd gi\u00fap c\u00e1c c\u01a1 quan qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd, \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ea1y v\u00e0 h\u1ecdc, t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ra m\u1ed9t b\u1ed9 s\u00e1ch th\u00edch h\u1ee3p nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t d\u00f9ng chung cho c\u1ea3 n\u01b0\u1edbc (sau n\u00e0y). V\u1ec1 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn, mua s\u00e1ch gi\u00e1o khoa s\u1ebd g\u00e2y m\u00f4n kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n l\u1edbn cho h\u1ecdc sinh v\u00e0 gia \u0111\u00ecnh. M\u1eb7t kh\u00e1c chi ph\u00ed c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t b\u1ed9 s\u00e1ch m\u1edbi c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 r\u1ebb, g\u00e2y n\u00ean g\u00e1nh n\u1eb7ng v\u1ec1 kinh t\u1ebf cho nh\u1eefng gia \u0111\u00ecnh kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.<\/p>\n<p>Trong b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y, m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd g\u1eedi t\u1edbi c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n link file m\u1ec1m \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea3i s\u00e1ch to\u00e1n 10 c\u1ee7a 3 b\u1ed9 s\u00e1ch + gi\u1ea3i b\u00e0i t\u1eadp s\u00e1ch gi\u00e1o khoa lu\u00f4n. G\u1ed3m:<br \/>\n+ B\u1ed9 K\u1ebft n\u1ed1i tri th\u1ee9c v\u1edbi cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng<br \/>\n+ B\u1ed9 C\u00e1ch di\u1ec1u<br \/>\n+ B\u1ed9 Ch\u00e2n tr\u1eddi s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o.<\/p>\n<p>Sau \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 link t\u1eebng B\u1ed9 nha:<br \/>\nS\u00e1ch gi\u00e1o khoa (\u1ea5n v\u00e0o t\u00ean t\u1eebng b\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea3i nha): <a href=\"https:\/\/drive.google.com\/drive\/folders\/1Kg34-XZVboqVZHQF4gF7VQusM-1mwr12?usp=sharing\">B\u1ed9 K\u1ebft n\u1ed1i tri th\u1ee9c<\/a> <a href=\"https:\/\/drive.google.com\/drive\/folders\/1ZVISiZ1fB5AefQQr4tzkBm3_eEzUOxPN?usp=sharing\">B\u1ed9 C\u00e1nh di\u1ec1u<\/a> <a href=\"https:\/\/drive.google.com\/drive\/folders\/1a1ba5XuQRtjnN648sVXUlu9OBIPjyyiU?usp=sharing\">B\u1ed9 Ch\u00e2n tr\u1eddi s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o<\/a><br \/>\nS\u00e1ch gi\u1ea3i b\u00e0i t\u1eadp gi\u00e1o khoa (\u1ea5n v\u00e0o t\u00ean t\u1eebng b\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea3i nha): <a href=\"https:\/\/drive.google.com\/drive\/folders\/1HXKQo--YJRvGljPVSZTPZ_o3sIceLscT?usp=sharing\">B\u1ed9 K\u1ebft n\u1ed1i tri th\u1ee9c<\/a> <a href=\"https:\/\/drive.google.com\/drive\/folders\/1toMWULLZbXKnt9CxSoOTpH19zXGaC0pt?usp=sharing\">B\u1ed9 C\u00e1nh di\u1ec1u<\/a> <a href=\"https:\/\/drive.google.com\/drive\/folders\/1ROeZYYaLDApZBx7ijl_h2nkNMeQg1w_E?usp=sharing\">B\u1ed9 Ch\u00e2n tr\u1eddi s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o<\/a><\/p>\n<p>C\u00e1c b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea3i v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ec3 xem tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Ho\u1eb7c nh\u1eefng b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 mua s\u00e1ch m\u1edbi th\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea3i v\u1ec1 r\u1ed3i \u0111i in ra \u1ea1! Ch\u00fac c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n nh\u1ecf l\u1edbp 10 h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp th\u1eadt t\u1ed1t ha!!!<\/p>\n<!-- AddThis Advanced Settings generic via filter on the_content --><!-- AddThis Share Buttons generic via filter on the_content -->","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<div class=\"mh-excerpt\"><p>Xin ch\u00e0o c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n! M\u00ecnh l\u00e0 Th\u1ecf v\u00e0 m\u00ecnh l\u1ea1i \u0111\u0103ng t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e2y \u1ea1! C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n bi\u1ebft h\u1ebft <a class=\"mh-excerpt-more\" href=\"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/blog\/2022\/08\/05\/toan-10-sach-giao-khoa-giai-bai-tap-toan-10-file-loai-sach-moi\/\" title=\"To\u00e1n 10: S\u00e1ch gi\u00e1o khoa + gi\u1ea3i b\u00e0i t\u1eadp to\u00e1n 10 (file lo\u1ea1i s\u00e1ch m\u1edbi)\">[&#8230;]<\/a><!-- AddThis Advanced Settings generic via filter on get_the_excerpt --><!-- AddThis Share Buttons generic via filter on get_the_excerpt --><\/p>\n<\/div>","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":4283,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[7,9],"tags":[186,366,102,26],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4282"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thocaca.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=4282"}],"version-history":[{"count":5,"href":"https:\/\/thocaca.co